OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FIt was a dramatic night in Jersey's
OL,7,Felection with some big names in
OL,8,Fpolitics failing to secure a seat in
OL,9,Fthe next States Assembly.
OL,11,FHere are some of the biggest names to
OL,12,Fmiss out:
OL,14,FThe former leader of Reform Jersey,
OL,15,FSam Mezec, lost his seat and came 10th
OL,16,Fin the Senatorial vote, missing out by
OL,17,F2,197 votes.
OL,19,FMr Mezec was first elected in 2014 as
OL,20,Fa Deputy of St Helier. Since then, he
OL,21,Fhas been re-elected three times.
