OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FReform was initially founded as a
OL,7,Fpressure group in 2012 to campaign for
OL,8,Felectoral reform in the run up to the
OL,9,F2013 referendum.
OL,11,FThe party first stood in the 2014 by-
OL,12,Felections, where it won two seats. It
OL,13,Fofficially registered as a political
OL,14,Fparty in July 2014 to compete in the
OL,15,F2014 general election.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
