OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FIn the last assembly, Mr Mezec was
OL,7,Felected as Deputy of St. Helier South.
OL,8,FHe held the role of Chair of Corporate
OL,9,FServices Scrutiny Panel, the President
OL,10,Fof Scrutiny Liaison Committee, and
OL,11,Fchaired the Future Hospital Review
OL,12,FPanel.
OL,14,FSince the change of government in
OL,15,F2024, he has been Minister for Housing.
OL,17,FSteve Luce failed in his bid for
OL,18,FSenator placing 11th out of 17 in the
OL,19,Frace, with only the top nine elected,
OL,20,Fhe lost out by 2,902 votes.
OL,26,@nD@[rr
