OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FPreviously a farmer, Steve Luce was
OL,7,Ffirst elected as Deputy of St Martin
OL,8,Fin 2011 and has been re-elected three
OL,9,Ftimes.
OL,11,FHe has held numerous positions in that
OL,12,Ftime including Minister for Planning
OL,13,Fand chairing the Economic Affairs
OL,14,FScrutiny Panel. Most recently, he has
OL,15,Fbeen Minister for the Environment.
OL,17,FDavid Warr was bidding to become
OL,18,FConstable of St Helier but placed
OL,19,Fthird behind Inna Gardiner and Rob
OL,20,FWard.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
