OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FMr Warr was first elected as Deputy of
OL,7,FSt Helier South and quickly became
OL,8,FMinister for Housing and Communities
OL,9,Funtil the change in government in
OL,10,F2024. He was replaced in that role by
OL,11,Fformer Reform Jersey leader Sam Mezec.
OL,13,FSince then, he has been a member of
OL,14,Fthe Environment, Housing, and
OL,15,FInfrastructure Scrutiny Panel and the
OL,16,FPublic Accounts Committee.
OL,26,@sD@brr
