OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FMr Warr also attracted attention
OL,7,Fduring a campaign for the 'Love Our
OL,8,FLido' charity. Last year, he called
OL,9,Ffor a review into the Havre de Pas
OL,10,FLido tender process.
OL,12,FHe ran a campaign focused on Financial
OL,13,FStability and a "long term" vision.
OL,14,FOutside of politics, he is the owner
OL,15,Fof the Cooper & Co. coffee business.
OL,17,FMike Jackson
OL,26,@uD@QOUuD@[O]
