OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FMike Jackson was the serving
OL,7,FConnetable of St Brelade and lost that
OL,8,Fposition to Steve Pallett. He was
OL,9,Ffirst elected in 2005 and was Minister
OL,10,Ffor Transport before stepping back
OL,11,Ffrom politics in 2011.
OL,13,FHe was re-elected in 2018 and 2022 and
OL,14,Fwas the Chair of the Comite des
OL,15,FConnetables.
OL,17,FOutside of politics, Mr Jackson is the
OL,18,Fowner of a boatyard and Post Office in
OL,19,Fthe parish.
OL,21,FRaluca Kovacs
OL,26,@oD@ErrvD@[rrwD@Err
