OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FIncumbent St Saviour Deputy Raluca
OL,7,FKovacs failed to retain her position,
OL,8,Fwith only five candidates standing in
OL,9,Fthe District, which elects four
OL,10,FDeputies.
OL,12,FShe is a British Romanian, has lived
OL,13,Fin Jersey for over 17 years. Ms Kovacs
OL,14,Fwas elected in 2022 with previous
OL,15,Fexperience in customer service and
OL,16,Fbanking, and was recognised as the
OL,17,F'Commonwealth New Parliamentarian of
OL,18,Fthe Year' in 2024.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
