OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FThe Reform Deputy has lost her post to
OL,7,FMalcolm Ferey, Louise Doublet, Chris
OL,8,FLeck and Robert Parker.
OL,10,FKevin Lewis
OL,12,FFor the first time in more than two
OL,13,Fdecades, Kevin Lewis will not
OL,14,Frepresent St Saviour.
OL,16,FFirst elected in 2005, he served as a
OL,17,Fmember of the Economic Affairs
OL,18,FScrutiny Panel and later as both
OL,19,FMinister for Transport and
OL,20,FInfrastructure. He served for 17 years
OL,21,Fas the District's Deputy.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
