OL,3,CWho's out? The biggest losers in
OL,4,CJersey's election
OL,6,FIn 2022, Mr Lewis was narrowly elected
OL,7,Fas Constable for St Saviour, but
OL,8,Ffinished last in this year's election,
OL,9,Fbehind both David Curtis, and Suzanne
OL,10,FWebb.
OL,12,FJohn Le Fondre
OL,14,FIn this year's election, John Le
OL,15,FFondre was unsuccessful in his attempt
OL,16,Fto return to politics as Constable of
OL,17,FSt Lawrence, losing out to new
OL,18,Fcandidate Tina Palmer.
OL,26,@tD@NrrwD@Frr
